  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "chapterTitle": "序言",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300023509_5_3042-3084",
          "range": "3042-3084",
          "rangeStart": 3042,
          "rangeEnd": 3084,
          "markText": "一个国家，一个政权，如果内部安定团结的话，无论敌人势力怎样强大，也不见得会被消灭掉。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1736384958,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-01-09 09:09:18",
          "chapterUid": 5,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023509&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3042&rangeEnd=3084",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47e32d60813ab6faeg01919d?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3042&rangeEnd=3084"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "chapterTitle": "第一章　三国分立",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300023509_6_19328-19401",
          "range": "19328-19401",
          "rangeStart": 19328,
          "rangeEnd": 19401,
          "markText": "东汉王朝统治的崩溃，固然造成了四百年的分裂的局面，然而这一分裂，并没有使中国衰落，它只可算作是后来创造国家中央集权化的经济前提的一个准备阶段而已。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1736384950,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-01-09 09:09:10",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023509&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=19328&rangeEnd=19401",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47e32d60813ab6faeg01919d?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=19328&rangeEnd=19401"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300023509_6_545-627",
          "range": "545-627",
          "rangeStart": 545,
          "rangeEnd": 627,
          "markText": "在整个两汉时期，社会经济危机主要是由春秋战国以来土地自由买卖、土地的集中、奴隶使用数目的增加、小生产者——农民和手工业者经济的衰颓、流民的大量出现这些现象来构成的。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1736382329,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-01-09 08:25:29",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023509&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=545&rangeEnd=627",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47e32d60813ab6faeg01919d?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=545&rangeEnd=627"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
