      "totalCount": 1275,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023509&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=545&rangeEnd=627",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47e32d60813ab6faeg01919d?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=545&rangeEnd=627"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023509_6_19328-19401",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "19328-19401",
      "markText": "东汉王朝统治的崩溃，固然造成了四百年的分裂的局面，然而这一分裂，并没有使中国衰落，它只可算作是后来创造国家中央集权化的经济前提的一个准备阶段而已。",
      "totalCount": 960,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023509&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=19328&rangeEnd=19401",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47e32d60813ab6faeg01919d?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=19328&rangeEnd=19401"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023509_5_3042-3084",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3042-3084",
      "markText": "一个国家，一个政权，如果内部安定团结的话，无论敌人势力怎样强大，也不见得会被消灭掉。",
      "totalCount": 924,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023509&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3042&rangeEnd=3084",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47e32d60813ab6faeg01919d?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3042&rangeEnd=3084"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023509_9_10273-10328",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "10273-10328",
      "markText": "孙权看到大臣分成两派，恐怕自己身后也会像袁绍身后那样酿成大乱，就废太子和，并命令孙霸自杀，而立少子孙亮为太子。",
      "totalCount": 731,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023509&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10273&rangeEnd=10328",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47e32d60813ab6faeg01919d?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10273&rangeEnd=10328"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023509_5_4562-4640",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4562-4640",
      "markText": "尤其本人对马克思列宁主义学习不够，观点、方法都存在很多问题，希望历史学界的同志们，严予批评，如果我有第二次修改的机会，我一定遵循同志们提出的意见，再作修改。",
      "totalCount": 728,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023509&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4562&rangeEnd=4640",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47e32d60813ab6faeg01919d?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4562&rangeEnd=4640"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023509_6_2606-2629",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2606-2629",
      "markText": "法律贱商人，商人已富贵矣；尊农夫，农夫已贫贱矣",
      "totalCount": 658,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023509&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2606&rangeEnd=2629",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47e32d60813ab6faeg01919d?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2606&rangeEnd=2629"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023509_5_3294-3346",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3294-3346",
      "markText": "只要自己内部安定团结，别人就不敢轻易欺侮，在中国历史上，这类例子还很多。这个历史教训，我们应该好好记取。",
      "totalCount": 646,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023509&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3294&rangeEnd=3346",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47e32d60813ab6faeg01919d?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3294&rangeEnd=3346"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023509_6_10907-10974",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "10907-10974",
      "markText": "汉政府趁这个胜利的军事形势，放手屠杀，史称“州郡所诛，一郡数千人”（《资治通鉴》汉灵帝中平元年）。这样，在全国范围内，又杀了几十万人。",
      "totalCount": 636,
